437
00:20:45,690 --> 00:20:46,920
In this case,

438
00:20:48,810 --> 00:20:49,780
either there is something

439
00:20:50,510 --> 00:20:51,200
particularly dishonorable

440
00:20:51,200 --> 00:20:52,680
about his past,

441
00:20:52,930 --> 00:20:54,120
or it makes him particularly miserable

442
00:20:54,160 --> 00:20:55,520
