446
00:21:01,730 --> 00:21:03,650
It's not that I have to know.

447
00:21:03,750 --> 00:21:04,520
I just think

448
00:21:04,520 --> 00:21:06,000
his attitude is wrong.

449
00:21:06,570 --> 00:21:07,440
What does he

450
00:21:07,440 --> 00:21:08,400
have to hide from me?

451
00:21:09,220 --> 00:21:10,360
Isn't our relationship

452
00:21:10,360 --> 00:21:12,000
